Ruffer LLP is an investment management firm. It offers services to private clients, trusts, pensions funds, corporate and charitable institutions. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income markets and manages mutual funds. It was established in 1994 and… MoreRuffer LLP is an investment management firm. It offers services to private clients, trusts, pensions funds, corporate and charitable institutions. The firm invests in the public equity, fixed income markets and manages mutual funds. It was established in 1994 and is located in London, UK.






